Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years have passed\Nsince the Paramount War at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew\Nreturned to Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And on their way\Nto the next stage—the New World—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they reached Fishman Island\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they were suddenly attacked\Nby the New Fishman Pirates—separating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others were rescued by Mermaids\Nand were brought to Camie's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time! Anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody please! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Donate blood to Sanji!
