Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Spare him some blood! My friend is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone with blood type S RH negative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time! Please donate blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,We beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Sanji-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult for humans\Nto get a blood transfusion on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Luffy-chin\Nand the others will keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Even though we're searching so hard,\Nwe still can't find anyone who'll donate blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna give up!\NThere has to be somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! I found a human over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This barrel arrived with Camie's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Liquor? Maybe treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but they sure sealid it up tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we open it in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're well-prepared, Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in town at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chin, you've lost most of your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that we found some donors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get up so fast!\NYou need to rest more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But why won't the Fishmen donate blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked all over town\Nbut we couldn't find any humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost gave up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, thanks for doing that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was I and what was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.87,Alt,,0,0,0,,No, don't think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want you to bleed out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Sanji! Let me introduce the blood donors we found at a bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't tell me I got blood\Nfrom such a delicate lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! We're all humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help each other in times of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can give you more, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:37.24,Alt,,0,0,0,,We can give you more, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that he's back to his old self!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you gotta thank them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, let me see your right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A positive reaction to poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You've been injected with venom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nwhen I fought against the Fishmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt something sting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This poison's really strong.\NAre you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Antibody must've developed in your body\Nto counter this kind of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been poisoned before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at Impel Down I almost got poisoned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisoned to death?\NThat's nothing to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The swordsman with the octopus legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He blocked my punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's pretty strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's coming from the cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Mermaids sure are noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are all messed-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I accidentally poisoned Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in trouble if he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly and the others were screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard them around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard them talking about opening a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, come here.\NThere's someone I'd like you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner of the Mermaid Cafe.\NShe let us borrow the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.39,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Is the blond boy okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.26,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(705,750,\1a&H00&)}Owner of the Mermaid Cafe\NMadame Sharley
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.26,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(750,0)\4a&HFF&}Owner of the Mermaid Cafe\NMadame Sharley
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.26,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. But since you're such a beautiful lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's best you stay away from the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's not tell Sanji-chin this place\Nis the back room of the Mermaid Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His doctor, Chopper-chin, said that\Nif he finds out, he'll have another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange prognosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Madame Sharley, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that, Straw Hat boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a crystal ball.\NIt's used for fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame's precognition is famous in Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not practicing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is usually best left unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about this? Do Mermaids poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with telling fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Apologize to her, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie, you can take a day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You always work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,these days we don't have human pirates as guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so my business is drying up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls from the cove\Nwill be coming soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have enough\Nstar waitresses to handle customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough star... fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I should have delivered those clams to Pappagu by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so out-of-context!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Monsieur Pappagu is having fun\Nat the cafe with an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At the cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't mention this in front of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but when Madame was a little child,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,she predicted many pirates would start coming to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a year before the Great Pirate Era began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Among a host of other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,she recently predicted the war at Marineford
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and Whitebeard's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't stand knowing what bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's taking care of Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-chin! Usopp-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.39,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the main street of Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That's the entrance of the Mermaid Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a {\i1}cafe{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have food too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cakes and sea fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We Merfolk don't eat meat or fish
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so the menu has things like Kelp Brûlée,\NSeaweed Tart, Kelp Soufflé...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they even edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we have meat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shellfish meat! Scallop Sandwich, Freshwater Clam Pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shellfish isn't meat!\NHow dare you disrespect meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Anyway, let's get going!\NTo the Mermaid Cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Pappagu will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look down on meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Resting my bones! Resting my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:08.97,Alt,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Luffy-san and Usopp-san! And it's been a while, Camie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I look at your panti—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw! Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}you{\i0} were with Pappagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I didn't expect to be rescued by Pappagu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was just as much of a surprise for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was trying to perfect an idea\Nfor a new design at the cove,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw some bones\Ndrifting towards me in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul King, come see us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a wonderful time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back, beautiful Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like they took my backbone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, but if I lose my bones, I'll have nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't care if I die today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He got so worked up over the cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wonder what's going on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't leaving today, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are interested in the cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can come back with everybody later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna take Bones back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me! Do you like sea monster meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wild, I don't wanna eat seaweed or shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My main food is savage sea monster meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pappagu, I almost forgot! Here are your clams for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Camie's best clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} eat shellfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful! Elegant! Wonderful! Sniff, sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.14,Alt,,0,0,0,,I wonder how they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Merfolk, Fishmen eat meat and fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of that kinda food to go around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just what I was looking for! Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a ghost—why are they looking for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wasn't this guy on the ghost ship we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You guys saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole nation's been looking for him for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pirate—an undersea bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about it later. Get on first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vander Decken was sending love letters\Nto the Mermaid Princess of Ryugu Kingdom every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, the letters became packages,\Nthen threats demanding her hand in marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's fluffy! Feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's fluffy! Feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's like heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His eccentric behavior made the Mermaid Princess\Nafraid and it became of national concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, the Mermaid Princess' father,\NKing Neptune, got mad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and those three princes you met earlier mobilized the army to chase after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but they can't find him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie, Camie... I was just telling them about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune, the God of the Sea,\Nwho runs this country
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,has four children\Nincluding the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Princess is the youngest and the three princes are older than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Camie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I can't understand is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Deck must be a ghostly pirate\Nfrom hundreds of years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those legends are often exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly existed and in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the legendary captain, Vander Decken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,reached Fishman Island and died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship you saw was\Nthe Flying Dutchman, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his descendant who's on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vander Decken IX!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! His descendant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That means he's not a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Being only bones, and thinking I'd met a real ghost,\NI was starting to feel more dead than alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie... Camie... Camie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look closer,\NMerfolk and Fishmen are all pretty different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's old Mermaids!\NJust like Grandma Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The dad's a Fishman, but his children are both Merfolk and Fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Mermaid and Fishman get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,their kids could be either\NMerfolk or Fishman, boy or girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are four possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, so that's why they're all different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a candy factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, why is there a pirate flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That? You can see the same flag\Nat the island's entrance and at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That flag is protecting Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mark belongs to a pirate\Ncalled Charlotte Linlin of the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's also known as Big Mom, one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Four Emperors?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the war, the island\Nwas under Whitebeard's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But nowadays it's Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But she demands a lot of sweet candies\Nevery month in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the factory is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Candies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This country can't exist\Nwithout the protection of those powerful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how dangerous this place is, where pirates come and go so frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's protecting the country in old man Whitebeard's place .
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Big Mom a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard never demanded anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe for Big Mom it's just business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Four Emperors like Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if I'll meet her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Fishverly Hills, the town of celebs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That tall building right in front of us is Pappagu's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That?! That's way too much for a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Madame from the Mermaid Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Madame Sharley?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so distressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Madame! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The pirate boy with the straw hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him out of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a precognition again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But something felt off about him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so I couldn't help looking into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! What'd you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharley! Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.21,Alt,,0,0,0,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be wrong!\NPlease, let my vision be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A human wearing a straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At Straw Hat Luffy's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,at his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,destroyed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island shines with beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But history has shrouded it in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hating humans, they desire retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They make their move, deep underneath the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Luffy and his crew run amok at Pappagu's shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the king of Fishman Island,\NNeptune himself, descends from his palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"The King of Fishman Island\NNeptune, the God of the Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
